HEADWORD: Pink
<hw>Pink</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D.
<ets>pink</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>A vessel with a very
narrow stern; -- called also <altname>pinky</altname>.</def> <rj><au>Sir
W. Scott.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Pink stern</b></col> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>, <cd>a narrow
stern.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pink</ent>⟦br⟧

